f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 準備下年冬天去🤔想問下有冇巴打去過<br />\n同埋係咪好難見到極光?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為北極光會受天氣影響，其實要睇運氣。9月底10月初最好，可以順便睇紅葉。</blockquote><br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋想問係咪要預多幾日時間睇極光?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇得到2日1 夜都夠，睇唔到幾多日都唔會夠<br />\n<br />\n好睇彩數。"},{"pid":"afa06c618fff3c7819a127361b25f12982e6d050","tid":121024,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T02:59:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"91f4f3cff71fef7c59958a37fdcf8baa31892de3","tid":121024,"uid":46399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T03:01:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打淨係打算睇極光定咩?</blockquote><br />\n主要想睇極光🤔"},{"pid":"a1d292fdc977ab2f6c70f415292bf71348d29fda","tid":121024,"uid":46399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T03:02:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 準備下年冬天去🤔想問下有冇巴打去過<br />\n同埋係咪好難見到極光?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為北極光會受天氣影響，其實要睇運氣。9月底10月初最好，可以順便睇紅葉。</blockquote><br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋想問係咪要預多幾日時間睇極光?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇得到2日1 夜都夠，睇唔到幾多日都唔會夠<br />\n<br />\n好睇彩數。</blockquote><br />\n試過第一晚就見到大爆發,成個天都係 好震撼<br />\n<br />\n之後book tour 諗住睇多次,點知3日都因為天氣問題cancel 左</blockquote><br />\n一定要join tour定點🤔"},{"pid":"2bc75f6cdc7d7ab04dadfa5caa235fea2a6c7601","tid":121024,"uid":42435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T03:05:43.000Z","msg":"跟支那團，睇唔到可以打柒導遊回水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51abee01f8657f6613a462f680eef75eab68f8b7","tid":121024,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T03:08:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>跟支那團，睇唔到可以打柒導遊回水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n賠埋香港過去機票，好過買旅遊保。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57fe902f2e6a121643b9b6277b1ef09b1f31d0c5","tid":121024,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T03:09:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"46991b53b6c1455e80580255f27917f5d3c6b429","tid":121024,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T03:10:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce939411f9420ee8eb1a8d43e1f24a2550fb031c","tid":121024,"uid":55416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T03:16:29.000Z","msg":"早幾年去芬蘭<br />\n天氣太差<br />\n追咗幾晚都睇唔到極光<br />\n<br />\n我都打算之後去加拿大睇<br />\n不過我自己就寧願去到跟local tour<br />\n人哋乜都預備晒兼車你去車你走<br />\n嗰啲鐘數應該眼瞓到仆街"},{"pid":"e5b512a261d7afdc398bce912ca8fd8d5dec01d4","tid":121024,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T03:25:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3157211415402511af00c00f53cc048f3f86ae2b","tid":121024,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T03:26:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"923b5265aba0aea24ae7e7066781958c1c1d1b6a","tid":121024,"uid":49776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T05:25:27.000Z","msg":"幾大都租車<br />\n想幾時去幾時走都得，<br />\n又可以去多幾個唔同地方<br />\nbtw遊客要去試下Bullock's Bistro同鹿肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29577602da1a1b825c7b6835aa541440bec15b7d","tid":121024,"uid":39346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T05:33:37.000Z","msg":"聖誕去完<br />\n4晚中 3晚半 (果半出得半個鐘同好弱)"}]}